author: Top Gear
description:
Red Bull’s RB17 hypercar promises lap times equivalent to F1. Let that sink in… But before the time comes to test our necks against the g-forces, we popped along to see the bespoke 4.5-litre V10 scream on the dyno, to see the new factory where the RB17 will be built, and to see what Red Bull’s hypercar will look like in finished form.

🚗 Red Bull RB17
🎤 Ollie Kew
